milestones.description: Wasim Raja has broken the record for most sixes (9) in ODIs for PAK, going past Zaheer Abbas's 8
Derek Randall has broken the record for most catches (16) in ODIs for ENG, going past Graham Gooch's 15
Iqbal Qasim has conceded the most runs in an innings (76) in ODIs for PAK, going past Sarfraz Nawaz's record of 71
Dickie Bird has broken the record for officiating the most ODIs (18) as an umpire, going past Constant
This is the highest match aggregate (517) involving teams England & Pakistan in ODIs
Wasim Raja has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (33) for PAK, going past Javed Miandad
Imran Khan and Wasim Raja's 60-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Imran Khan and Wasim Raja
